text: José Antonio Carrasco Ramírez (born 8 September 1980 in Madrid) is a former Spanish cyclist. ==Palmarès== ;2005 :1st stage 3a Vuelta a Extremadura ;2006 :1st Vuelta Ciclista a León ;2007 :1st stage 2 Volta a Coruña ;2012 :1st stage 1 GP Abimota ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Madrid Category:Vuelta a España cyclists
